---
title: Double Sesame-Hoisin Pork Noodles & Sautéed Veg with Fried Eggs & Crispy Shallots
description: Saucy, slurp-worthy noodles coated in a rich sesame dressing and hoisin sauce, topped with a crispy fried egg and crunchy shallots—this dish is a total flavour bomb! Sweet, savoury, and packed with umami, it’s the perfect mix of comfort and crunch in every bite.

